title: Hummingbird cake
ingredients: ['375g plain flour', '375g caster sugar', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1 teaspoon salt', '350ml rapeseed oil', '3 eggs', '1 (220g) tin pineapple, drained and pureed', '450g mashed bananas', '120g chopped black walnuts', 'Icing', '1 (200g) tub cream cheese, softened', '110g butter, softened', '450g icing sugar', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract']
